        title: 'FŌMESI SILIVA',
        content:
            "NE MANA FATULISI ‘A E TONGA KOTOA POLOTIKAASI MEI HE MINONETI KOULA KO E ‘EVA LUSIA Ē ‘ATOMI KUONGA KO E TUNAMENI ‘O E SIALEVINI KE OMA \n\n PIUTAU Ē NGAAHI KAKALA ‘ILOA FOLA MOE ‘EFINANGA KI HE HINGOA KAE FOLANAKI ‘A E TAUNGAPEKA HE MUNA E ‘UTUFÖMESI SILIVA \n\n NEU TELEVISONE HE SATELAITE KI FÄ`ONELUA MO E TONGI`ONE ‘ASI HO KOFU KAPIKAPI MATA‘ITOFE MOHO TEKITEKI SĪ LAVE‘I TAVAKE \n\n UISA NEU VISONE HE‘EKU MOHE KI SI‘O NGOUE FATAKI ‘I PAPILONE MATALA‘I ‘AKAU ‘OKU TAHA PE NE PAKI‘I MEI HE FALA ‘O SETANE \n\n TAU FUNGA MAHOFÄ TEU MATE VALELAU HO‘O UINI KAE POINI ‘A POUVALU ‘OKU LEKOOTI KI HE PÄ ‘A NGANGALU UISA ‘OKU AKE ‘EKU MANATU KOE ‘ULI PË ‘O E VAO TAMANU SI‘OMAU LIKU KO VALE FANAU"),
    Book1(
